content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4815.15 - Transaction of business during conduct of bingo prohibited

State Regulations

All licensed bingo suppliers, their duly authorized
agents, salesmen and representatives are forbidden to be present during the
conduct of bingo for the transaction of business, except if authorized by the
licensed authorized organization. Notes
